when the solomon family moves into an old south dakota farmhouse , in yet another attempt by dad ( dylan mcdermott ) to reconnect with the family , especially with their formerly drunk - driving daughter jessica ( the underrated kristen stewart ) , in the more subtle countryside than their home in chicago .
