so , in guys and dolls , " my time of day " describes the adventurous life of sky masterson as it is about to be compromised by the most unlikely woman .
every song in this brilliant exemplar of the genre sets a mood , or develops a character , creating a phantasmagoria of place , turned absolutely believable by the self disclosing evocations of song .
